    • Constructor Detail

      • WriteBytesProvider

        public WriteBytesProvider(Generator generator,
                  Callback flushCallback)
        Create a WriteBytesProvider with specified Generator and "flush" Callback.
        Parameters:
        generator - the generator to use for converting Frame objects to network ByteBuffers
        flushCallback - the flush callback to call, on a write event, after the write event has been processed by this WriteBytesProvider.

        Used to trigger another flush of the next set of bytes.
